---
import ContentLayout from "@/layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout title="Privacy Policy — Verscienta Health" description="How we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-earth-50 via-sage-50/50 to-cream-100 dark:from-earth-950 dark:via-earth-900/50 dark:to-earth-950 border-b border-sage-200/50 dark:border-earth-700">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-earth-100 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-earth-300">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 prose prose-earth dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as when you create an account, submit a contact form, or use the symptom checker. This may include your name, email address, and health-related queries.</p>
    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use collected information to provide and improve our services, respond to inquiries, and send educational content when requested. Symptom checker queries are anonymized before processing.</p>
    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption in transit (TLS), HTTP-only authentication cookies, and CSRF protection on all forms.</p>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use third-party services including Cloudflare (CDN and security), MeiliSearch (search), and xAI (AI symptom analysis). Each service has its own privacy policy. Symptom data sent to AI services is anonymized.</p>
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:privacy@verscienta.com">privacy@verscienta.com</a>.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@verscienta.com">privacy@verscienta.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</ContentLayout>
